Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:04.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the biggest daikon \Nin the entire shared field?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It will be tough to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:07.88,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Straight like a bee on an autumn road.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:15.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he has marched in small steps for 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:18.98,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,He is dragging \Nthe daikon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.00,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,It will bruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, the syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he will cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once he starts crying he can go on for 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, don't cry, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\clip(356,651,579,697)\t(0,1200,\clip(550,653,724,710))\pos(640,700)}Mommy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He promised his mom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,not to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:52.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do not cry, do not cry. \N Today I will not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I have decided not to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:22:00.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Using the spare bag that the mother packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.68,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,The mother \N is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:10.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the mother said: "if you feel like crying \Nthen look at mount Fuji."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All good. I won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is the daikon alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's no good if it becomes small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HF65D00&\pos(1016.503,536.764)}Don't cry \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N   Don't cry \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N \N   Don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.75,TextOver,,0,0,0,,{\pos(292.45,157.141)\c&HF65D00&}But the daikon \N is disappearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:28.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having overcome the urge to cry \N the heavy carrying Shougo has come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:30.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? Is the daikon alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:33.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hasn't it become small?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:39.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's chafing, it's chafing. \NIt's chafing on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:42.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It sure was a big daikon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's being grated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The beige house over there is sister Chi's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:53.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is mother's cousin so they often come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:55.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh noes, there is a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fs66.667\pos(556.928,114.789)}Woof
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Got to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:03.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\clip(166,651,356,697)\t(0,1200,\clip(356,653,762,710))\pos(640,704)}I dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\clip(166,651,356,697)\t(0,1200,\clip(356,653,857,710))\pos(640,704)}The bag ripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:08.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Have to overcome the disaster. \N Won't cry this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:09.26,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,Admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:11.67,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646.328,566.343)\fad(200,200)}Malt daikon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:15.72,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,He can't carry \N all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He even became able to carry the entire daikon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:22.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He sure has dragged it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:23.24,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,So short.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:26.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Facing his fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes. I made it safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:36.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Phew, arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:41.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why is he still holding two?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:44.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,, I see, for Runa's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pass the scary dog again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't look, don't look
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:52.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. If I don't look it won't be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:58.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\clip(166,651,356,697)\t(0,1800,\clip(356,653,952,710))\fad(0,200)\pos(640,706)}Runa's house is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No one is here so I will just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:03.42,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,This is where \N he leaves it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(375.219,107.47)}Shou?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(857.139,150.907)}Where is \N your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:09.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Runa's mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,, Mom is home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:11.86,TextOver,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846.225,151.023)}You came \N by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so amazing. I got a phone call about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,0:24:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When it runs out I will personally bring you some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.92,0:24:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You came by yourself? \N That's remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:26.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}This is Runa who is the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:28.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.56,0:24:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636.914,520.623)}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.98,0:24:33.55,WhitePinkBorder,,0,0,0,,{\clip(455,520,486,583)\pos(634.914,582.364)\t(0,1000,\clip(453,531,815,589))}He will arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.55,0:24:35.39,WhitePinkBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634.914,578.975)\fad(0,200)}Walk properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:35.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(253.457,130.034)}Suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.20,0:24:37.38,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.02,0:24:38.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please don't arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:40.56,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930.69,281.07)}Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.62,0:24:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.66,0:24:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother has called Chi and explained that something nice will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(640,55)}TN: Not actually his sister. He uses a honorific used \Nfor someone who is like an older sister figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.23,0:24:53.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(812.185,421.211)\fad(0,200)}Sister \N Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.37,0:24:56.07,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(617.787,552.512)\fad(200,0)}Malt daikon here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.26,0:24:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you Shougo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:24:59.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? It's the daikon from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:03.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, despite all his hardships it has become this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.78,0:25:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you bring it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.22,0:25:06.56,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,From the nursery school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nursery school?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.04,0:25:08.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.28,0:25:09.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It used to be the biggest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou, you brought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.26,0:25:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.417,304.571)}It has become \N grated daikon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.22,0:25:16.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mana has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.00,0:25:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us how you cut it at your home. Let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.34,0:25:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful of your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.34,0:25:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.82,0:25:31.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Indeed, this is how you put it in. \NJust like how your mother taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.22,0:25:38.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,5 minutes later. \NWow, we put more daikon in it than mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878.827,113.362)}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.62,0:25:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(874.459,356.665)}the juice
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Shougo brought this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.40,0:25:47.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This will help cure your cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.70,0:25:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}She licked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.12,0:25:51.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if it doesn't taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.10,0:25:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it out like you always do with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.40,0:25:59.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did the mother's errand succeed or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:00.76,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.76,0:26:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:07.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not scared of a simple dog anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:09.68,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(633.059,555.288)}I am not afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.32,0:26:11.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,See? I am composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.14,0:26:14.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe a bit scared still.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:17.92,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.54,0:26:20.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shougo has grown a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi called mother right away and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.28,0:26:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"He was such a cry baby yesterday \N what he accomplished today really surprised me."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.90,0:26:29.80,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.98,0:26:39.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He returns home bigger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.91,0:26:41.54,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\move(761.905,304.762,171.429,209.524)}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:44.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.26,0:26:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.80,0:26:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}Did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.60,0:26:48.28,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.28,0:26:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.56,0:26:52.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}Mom, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.66,0:26:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716.356,268.12)}Awesome. It's so amazing that you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752.451,334.71)}Did you cry, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.26,0:26:58.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660.825,605.23)}I totally did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou, you might be greater than mount Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.36,0:27:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:06.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:08.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dad will be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.80,0:27:15.18,TextOver,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\fad(200,200)\pos(888.105,129.728)}Nine years
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.28,0:27:15.18,TextOver,,0,0,0,,{\fs57.143\fad(200,200)\pos(474.533,456.316)}later
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:15.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,Was it really \N that long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}Are you always preparing the daikon like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.15,0:27:26.92,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&HA53819&\pos(546.421,249.021)\fad(200,0)}Shougo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.15,0:27:26.92,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&HA53819&\pos(165.158,384.2)\fad(200,0)}13 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.38,0:27:26.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shougo is in 2nd grade of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.16,0:27:29.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can even grate daikon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.79,0:27:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(983.966,156.722)}So you like \N to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.46,0:27:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it relatively.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.10,0:27:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(991.236,156.444)} On what \Noccasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.10,0:27:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When my mother is (coming home) late.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.63,0:27:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think about what I want to make for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.47,0:27:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will peek into the fridge and notice potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.14,0:27:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I start to wonder what can be made with potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.28,0:27:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will look into it and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.30,0:27:50.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He finds it on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.30,0:27:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you want to make this for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.34,0:27:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Because she is always working so hard on her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.36,0:28:00.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mix potatoes, starch and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.86,0:28:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is today's meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.03,0:28:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928.764,568.836)}It's imo (potato) mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.36,0:28:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Imomochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.26,0:28:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mash the potatoes until soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.43,0:28:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(513.665,151.796)}If you don't \N straighten it thin
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.84,0:28:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(123.274,147.322)}it will become \N like powder
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:15.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.22,0:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(403.048,153.67)}I make \Nit round
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.74,0:28:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.204,149.669)}and stretch \N it thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.08,0:28:19.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He puts cheese in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.81,0:28:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(469.124,155.728)}Instead of \N salad oil
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(155.158,157.935)}I usually \Nuse butter
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.95,0:28:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(468.017,146.375)}The flavor \N is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.02,0:28:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(129.77,141.705)}which makes \N it delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:29.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's done after being heated on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.82,0:28:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(854.03,115.208)}It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.20,0:28:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's imomochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.80,0:28:33.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.89,0:28:36.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.223,537.253)\fad(200,0)}It's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.89,0:28:36.06,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635.834,581.646)\fad(200,0)}Shou-made 「Imomochi」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.42,0:28:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm home. \N- Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:42.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today, mother comes home all happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.48,0:28:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.34,0:28:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad({200,0)\pos(438.747,198.398)}We will add \N grated daikon \N for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.70,0:28:50.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They also add grated daikon?
