Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.48,0:29:16.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is in 5th grade in primary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.97,0:29:17.73,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(925.987,366.617)\c&H0B0CA0&\fad(200,0)}Mana
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.82,0:29:18.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.74,0:29:21.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is destined to eat what Shougo makes for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.68,0:29:25.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Be honest if it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.51,0:29:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz327.2\pos(688.798,87.691)}Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.04,0:29:28.26,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056.907,680.387)\frz337.3}Delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.34,0:29:31.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has become somewhat better at complimenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.96,0:29:35.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I also want to meet Runa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:37.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So I decided to call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Runa?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.58,0:29:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They've come so...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.58,0:29:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What will do you? Can you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.28,0:29:44.03,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\fs38.095\pos(1130.065,363.842)}Right away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.16,0:29:46.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That embarrassing thing years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.30,0:29:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait 10 to 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.32,0:29:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,10 to 15 minutes? Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.40,0:29:55.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We decided to go over there instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.14,0:29:59.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Runa is also in 2nd grade of middle school. \N They are in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:07.78,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(423.427,380.49)\c&H131382&\fad(200,0)}Runa
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.14,0:30:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,'day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.14,0:30:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28.571\pos(640,65)}TN: It's worth noting that they use san next to her name - unlike what they did to Shougo - to treat her as an adult since she is a bit embarrassed by the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.22,0:30:06.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Runa.
