Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.02,0:30:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.38,0:30:12.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Yes, it's the same cameraman from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.48,0:30:17.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What will he introduce us to this time in the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.48,0:30:19.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seems like he has given up.
