Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.34,0:30:28.97,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\c&H1803B3&\pos(952.73,451.918)\frz16.83}buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.52,0:30:30.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember to put the recording equipment back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.94,0:30:39.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE82AC8&\pos(473.853,533.234)}What a plain-looking boombox.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.28,0:30:39.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We value our things. We have made the program for 20 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.58,0:30:40.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE82AC8&\\pos(590.834,363.823)}Isn't it too plain-looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.36,0:30:42.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The chair is new.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.42,0:30:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you use a nicer chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.40,0:30:46.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}Is it not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.24,0:30:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. The dreams. The children's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.18,0:30:52.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Little by little we have surpassed the 20 year anniversary for the first episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.93,0:30:56.00,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs47.619\c&HA82600&\4c&H3790C9&\pos(202.596,512.905)}It's like
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.93,0:30:56.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536.583,512.907)\c&H3790C9&\4c&H1516C0&}my own neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.93,0:30:56.00,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs47.619\c&HA82600&\4c&H3790C9&\pos(1006.198,512.907)}that you are filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:58.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's because we film from the perspective of a neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,640)}"My First Errand" is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:00.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No no.
