Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.90,0:31:05.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.50,0:31:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was gotcha again?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.40,0:31:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember! Choo choo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.70,0:31:16.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What was it again? Oh, it was that. Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.80,0:31:17.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fs38.095\c&H54DAE9&\4c&H1516C0&\frz19\fad(0,200)\3c&H220C64&\pos(228.543,458.836)}Roar with laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.80,0:31:17.32,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs57.143\pos(682.385,507.823)\fad(0,200)\3c&H72121B&\c&HFAB4AD&}Presenting Gotcha
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.32,0:31:24.66,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982.463,341.8)\c&HA62701&\fad(200,200)}Tatsuya \N4 years
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.78,0:31:24.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This talkative brother just loves TV commercials
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:26.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and his little brother follows suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.96,0:31:30.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both the nursery school teachers and people from the neighborhood agree
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.04,0:31:34.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sacchan talks funny. That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.12,0:31:40.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their house is a store that's why he is so talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.64,0:31:41.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Helping out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,, Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.65,0:31:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(915.867,133.611)}Yes, put \Nit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.12,0:31:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here? Next to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.15,0:31:51.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,570.505)\clip(171,514,1116,581)}This is Sea bream {\alpha&HFF&}● Japanese butterfish ● Tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.35,0:31:51.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,570.505)\clip(171,514,1116,581)}This is Sea bream ● Japanese butterfish {\alpha&HFF&}● Tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.19,0:31:51.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,570.505)\clip(171,514,1116,581)}This is Sea bream ● Japanese butterfish ● Tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.58,0:31:57.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad thought up an errand to make him buy an important item used in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.38,0:32:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here Tatsuya, what has happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.90,0:32:06.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636.61,562.034)}The bulb has burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.44,0:32:09.07,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634.914,519.682)\3c&H1E1F5B&\c&H11EDC7&}LED Reflector Lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.48,0:32:11.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Has it happened again? Without the reflector lamp the sashimi won't look as appetizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.36,0:32:14.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mom has thought of an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.68,0:32:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(488.463,99.916)}There is no pacifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.56,0:32:20.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has been lost. He will have to buy a new one for his little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.22,0:32:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.42,0:32:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tacchan, can you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.59,0:32:23.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628.133,545.093)}I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.32,0:32:25.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.02,0:32:33.90,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(987.55,113.093)\c&H0D0EA0&\fad(200,0)}Home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.02,0:32:33.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.57,248.623)\fad(200,0)}Home center
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.02,0:32:33.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(543.364,556.952)\fad(200,0)}Drugstore
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.96,0:32:29.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will buy the lamp at the store with the red sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.28,0:32:32.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And a pacifier for his little brother at the drug store.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.56,0:32:41.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if Tatsuya is by himself he talks all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.60,0:32:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking, walking, walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.30,0:32:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,, If I keep walking
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.41,0:32:49.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\clip(499,522,539,564)\pos(656.954,565.423)\t(0,900,\clip(520,520,808,566))}won't I arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.66,0:32:52.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The name of the lamp is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.88,0:32:56.19,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(655.259,572.2)\fad(200,200)}Reflector lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.70,0:32:57.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Indeed, reflector lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.60,0:33:02.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We have told the store in advance that a camera man will come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.22,0:33:05.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But we haven't told them who will come and purchase what.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.58,0:33:08.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Please do as you always do" is what we told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.74,0:33:10.48,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,Sounds hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.00,0:33:13.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This person is the customer
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.32,0:33:15.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,even though he is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.26,0:33:19.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.00,0:33:21.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the shop personnel hasn't noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.50,0:33:25.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(656.954,573.893)\fad(200,200)}One of our reflector lamps burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.56,0:33:26.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Say it in a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.68,0:33:31.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(641.905,565.714)\fad(200,200)}Talking about the reflector lamp. It burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.44,0:33:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it burn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.70,0:33:35.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(663.735,560.341)\fad(200,200)}We are fishmongers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.70,0:33:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a fish store?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.24,0:33:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After it burned out we went into deep consideration about what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my mom said "go by yourself and get it".
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.10,0:33:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.57,168.434)}What did you \Ncome to \N purchase?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.57,0:33:48.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(643.389,572.198)}Reflector lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.97,0:33:50.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\fs57.143\pos(633.217,540.01)}Reflector lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.14,0:33:54.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I told you from the start that I want to buy a reflector lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.10,0:33:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over here. There.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:02.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You finally get it. Reflector lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.34,0:34:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it? Reflector lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.90,0:34:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.98,0:34:12.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's such a difficult thing to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.88,0:34:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the correct item but this product is slightly different from our usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.92,0:34:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there another kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:20.34,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.06,0:34:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a different one but...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.14,0:34:24.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.80,0:34:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was different but one burned out. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.32,0:34:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:33.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for going with it, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.76,0:34:38.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya's talking engine has been kickstarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.86,0:34:40.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Next is his brother's pacifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.66,0:34:42.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Not talkifier, pacifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.68,0:34:45.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A pacifier please. Remember to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.00,0:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.62,0:34:47.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.96,0:34:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha is totally lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.76,0:34:51.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gotcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.47,0:34:53.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(645.086,563.73)\fad(200,0)}Gotcha is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.24,0:34:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand "to lose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.26,0:35:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,*Mumbling* Rikuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:05.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rikuto...  gotcha... lost. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.35,0:35:07.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(40,800,\fscx150\fscy150,TRY)\pos(624.741,531.539)\fad(0,200)}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.60,0:35:10.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cameraman please make it clear. What is gotcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.80,0:35:12.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, some assistance please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.02,0:35:16.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's a pacifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:20.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Tatsuya doesn't get it. \NWhy don't you know gotcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.92,0:35:23.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Get me a real adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.58,0:35:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, can you take care of this customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.62,0:35:31.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Someone must know. Since there are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.21,0:35:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(1010.12,242.905)}Veteran \N shop employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:35.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,, Where is the gotcha? Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.85,0:35:40.15,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(626.436,567.116)\fad(200,200)}Rikuto's gotcha. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.34,0:35:44.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just as expected from a veteran. \NShe knows what a gotcha is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.54,0:35:49.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,, That's what we thought but then she just got another person from the back office.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.02,0:35:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.20,0:35:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.24,0:35:52.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.28,0:35:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.00,0:35:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he lost it. We can't find it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.96,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.20,0:36:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see. It's used for sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.40,0:36:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Used for sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.36,0:36:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a gotcha is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.54,0:36:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Used when sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.04,0:36:10.16,Studio - 4:3,,0,0,0,,Can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.26,0:36:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
